      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Negative balances can indeed be correct. Receives are only counted once they reach a certain confirmation level. But sends (including ones that use unconfirmed inputs) are always counted. So if you receive 50 BTC, and send 40 BTC, until the 50 BTC confirms, you have a balance of -40 BTC.",
